  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>This +1 striking @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.JQdwHECogcTzdd8R]{Ghost Touch} crossbow has an array of crystalline lenses and silver fittings along the stock and feels strangely light.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> envision</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per minute</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You aim through the crossbow's crystalline lenses, gaining imprecise vision onto the <em>Ethereal Plane</em> with a range of 60 feet in addition to your normal senses for the rest of your turn. While this effect lasts, your next Strike with the <em>spiritsight crossbow</em> can also affect targets on the Ethereal Plane during the first 60 feet of its flight.</p>"
